# Card — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/card.css`

## CSS Classes

### Base
`.acko-card` — border-radius `--radius-3xl`, overflow hidden.

### Variants

| Class | Fill | Stroke | Shadow |
|-------|------|--------|--------|
| `.acko-card-default` | `--color-card-bg` | `1px solid --color-card-border` | none |
| `.acko-card-outline` | `transparent` | `1px solid --color-card-outline-border` | none |
| `.acko-card-elevated` | `--color-card-elevated-bg` | none | `--shadow-card` |
| `.acko-card-demoted` | `--color-card-demoted-bg` | `1px solid --color-card-demoted-border` | none |

Design intent: On a `--color-surface` page, default cards use `--color-card-bg` fill with a `--color-card-border` stroke — the border is *lighter* than the fill, creating a floating highlight edge.

### Padding

| Class | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `.acko-card-pad-none` | 0 |
| `.acko-card-pad-sm` | `var(--space-3)` |
| `.acko-card-pad-md` | `var(--space-5)` |
| `.acko-card-pad-lg` | `var(--space-6)` |

### Sub-component Classes

| Class | Padding | Border | Layout |
|-------|---------|--------|--------|
| `.acko-card-header` | `padding-bottom: --space-4` | `border-bottom: 1px solid --color-border-subtle` | `flex`, `gap: --space-3` |
| `.acko-card-content` | `padding: --space-5 0` | none | block |
| `.acko-card-footer` | `padding-top: --space-4` | `border-top: 1px solid --color-border-subtle` | `flex`, `justify-content: flex-end`, `gap: --space-3` |
| `.acko-card-inset` | `padding: --space-3` | `1px solid --color-card-demoted-border` | `bg: --color-card-demoted-bg`, `border-radius: --radius-inset-lg` |

### Nested Radius Rule

Any rectangular child element (icon box, image, inset panel) uses `--radius-inset-lg`, NOT the card's outer radius.

**Exempt**: Buttons, badges, avatars — keep their own intentional radius.

## Dark Theme

Automatic via semantic token remapping. All `--color-card-*` tokens remap to dark values. Elevated variant uses `--shadow-card` which remaps to heavier dark shadow.
